<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />I kept silent; I kept back my words even from saying anything good,</para>

<para style="q1">and my pain grew worse.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />My heart became hot;</para>

<para style="q1">when I thought about these things, it burned like a fire.</para>

<para style="q1">Then finally I spoke.</para>
